Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura-san, Sakura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I want you to help the washing place.
