Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She moves onto step 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She finally heads to the kitchen. The number of dishes that come in during peak hours aren't a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep washing, keep washing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep doing the same task.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep doing that. And put the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In here.
