Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the busiest time right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This will never end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The dishes are a bit too piled up. I'll help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, stopping the flow of work is the worst thing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,However, watching from here, you're completely a part of the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:13:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry because I'm holding them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to start again alone.
