Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was finally getting used to serving people, but washing the dishes felt endless. The dishes kept coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Working at a ramen store is harder than being an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:23.47,White Telop,,0,0,0,,{\pos(652.000000,333.333333)}Ramen Meal
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah! It looks good. Itadakimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Itadakimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing you're able to say is, "It's good," right? That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good because you worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:05.20,White Telop,,0,0,0,,{\pos(634.666667,333.333333)}Gets Excited Talking About Their Favorite Drinks
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, a girl's talk? As expected, you're a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:16.52,White Telop,,0,0,0,,{\pos(915.333333,374.666667)}End of Break
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I washed the cups, so can you help me wipe them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you think about joining HKT?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, I was in the world of show business ever since I was child, and during that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't pass the HKT auditions, I was thinking of applying myself more to my studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that so? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:16:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,While watching AKB-san, I thought it was lovely being able to make people smile. That's why I auditioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Being supported and loved by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Grateful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Honestly grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you prepare the ingredients now. Take over for the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? You're going to make a newcomer prepare the ingredients?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll start preparing the onions for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll cut 7 kilograms worth of onions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to cut this... Have you ever used a knife before. Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? Seven kilograms of onions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's apparently enough to feed 300 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura-kun, will you be ok? That's impossible for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All you do is drop this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to do it so that there's some texture when you bite into the fried rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't finish in 15 minutes, I'm going to scold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,1-1-15 minutes?! Manager, I think that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, at least for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what a dangerous way of using your hands. Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fingers are in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't cut your hand, ok? It'll bleed and we won't be able to use it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you're sliding it. Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like you're dropping it, but like you're moving it forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right. Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's good! I've seen something like that on cooking shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh, it won't end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:56.00,White Telop,,0,0,0,,{\pos(637.333333,333.333333)}It's been 20 minutes since she began prepping
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:18:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 20 minutes since she began the task. The store manager is looking at her with forgiving eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But...{\alpha&HFF%}isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But...isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Although you're cutting onions, you're not teary-eyed at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The tears aren't coming at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably, um.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You normally get teary-eyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done. I'm done at three, so I'll be going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your trainer, Matsuno-kun, is done with her shift first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura-kun, will you really be ok with Matsuno-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really obedient and when you tell her to do something, she learns it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Her best quality is her smile. She has a really cute smile and her pureness shines through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:19:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be loved by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, but if you had to name her one quality you're not so sure of?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not being able to speak loudly. Of course speaking loudly and being lively are really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuno-kun, thank you! Your guidance was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That hat is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like it's going to take a while, so I'm making him help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 30 minutes since she began prepping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was decided that she wouldn't be able to finish on time alone, so one of the staff members, Nakanosono-kun, will help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you decide to work part-time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Part-time? That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, here at Ikkousha, it's lively and energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was drawn to that, so I applied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:51.20,White Telop,,0,0,0,,{\pos(637.333333,333.333333)}Asked About His Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't attend a lot of middle or high school. \N{\fs22.000000}[T/N]: He mumbles at the very end so I can't understand his reason why
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to do something to help those kinds of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a really lovely dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be nice if your lovely dream comes true, Nakanosono-kun. Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:17.55,White Telop,,0,0,0,,{\pos(653.333333,301.333333)}Six hours have passed since she started working
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyawaki-san, you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Bad luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't finish the prepping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your 6-hour shift at Ikkousha-san is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we were able to make something delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He makes fried rice with the onions Sakura-kun chopped up earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My onion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fried rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good! That's good! That was your brightest smile today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:13.72,White Telop,,0,0,0,,{\pos(738.666667,352.000000)}After the CM,\Nshe finally receives her payment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 6 hours since she started working. Her shift is finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll finally receive her long-awaited payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyawaki-san, thanks for your hard work. You're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your wages for today. Thank you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a lot of guts. That surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she might get crushed, especially at the washing area. The washing area is crazy, especially at a ramen store.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She never gave up and did it energetically.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for holding you all back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:21:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.77,0:22:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for today. You tried your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,4,800 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I earned this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.75,0:22:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my first time working part-time, and I didn't know just how hard it was going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.46,0:22:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only ever worked as an idol, so
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.02,0:22:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,washing the dishes was the hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When my heart was going to break doing that, my senpais told me that I could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, I was able to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really, hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I once again realize how hard it was working part-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:23:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She experienced the difficulties of working.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The happiness and enrichment she was able to obtain there. She capitalized on this experienced and leveled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.12,0:23:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be able to meet a new Miyawaki Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What does working part-time mean to Sakura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.17,0:23:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm able to grow more than the person I was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, it's business.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,
